I like her so much-- whatever.

00:25:20.980 --> 00:25:24.290
Like do they show emotional
capacity in any way?

00:25:24.290 --> 00:25:25.847
Those would be the two things.

00:25:25.847 --> 00:25:26.555
AUDIENCE: Thanks.

00:25:26.555 --> 00:25:27.040
KIRA ASATRYAN: Sure.

00:25:27.040 --> 00:25:28.471
DAVE MARKS: In
your book you say,

