00:25:42.667 --> 00:25:44.750
KIRA ASATRYAN: Yeah, it's
fascinating stuff to me.

00:25:44.750 --> 00:25:46.350
I also talk about
Kim Kardashian.

00:25:46.350 --> 00:25:47.940
There's some stuff
